examples.en: We sat in the third row.

examples.en: Rent costs two-thirds of my paycheck.
examples.ru: Я отдаю за квартиру две трети своей зарплаты.

examples.en: The office is on the third floor.

examples.en: C is the third letter in the alphabet.
That's the third time I've seen him today.
examples.ru: Я уже в третий раз за сегодня его вижу.
